The hole has ragged edges from which cling two small grey animals. Suddenly, one leaps from the tree and, spreading skin flaps between its legs, glides north.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM IN 0
It is full of matted leaves.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFTOUCH 0
